<div class="node clear-block clear ">
    <h2 class="title"><a href="/2010/10/05/distraction">“Distraction,” Simplicity, and Running Toward Shitstorms</a></h2>
  		<span class="submitted">
  		<a href="/people/merlin-mann">Merlin Mann</a>  |  Oct 5 2010	</span>

  <div class="content"><!-- google_ad_section_start --><p><img src="http://img.skitch.com/20101001-nx4uup4c66fp4r664mqs1irpk6.jpg" alt="Dr. Einstein goes into a little more detail." /></p>
<blockquote><p>It can scarcely be denied that the supreme goal of all theory is to make the irreducible basic elements as simple and as few as possible without having to surrender the adequate representation of a single datum of experience.</p>
<p>&mdash;Albert Einstein, &ldquo;<a href="http://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Albert_Einstein">On the Method of Theoretical Physics</a>&rdquo; (1934)</p>
</p></blockquote>
<p><strong>Context</strong>: Last week, I pinched off one of my typically woolly emails in response to an acquaintance whom I admire. He&rsquo;s a swell guy who makes things I love, and he'd written, in part, to express concern that my recent <a href="http://www.art-bin.com/art/omodest.html" title="'A Modest Proposal For Preventing The Children of Poor People in Ireland From Being A Burden to Their Parents or Country, and For Making Them Beneficial to The Public,' By Jonathan Swift">Swift</a> <a href="http://www.kungfugrippe.com/post/1169153343/only-you" title="Kung Fu Grippe: Introducing 'ū—': A Distraction-Free Writing Environment">impersonation</a> had been directed explicitly at something he'd made. Which, of course, it hadn&rsquo;t&mdash;but which, as I'll try to discuss here, strikes me as irrelevant.</p>
<p>To paraphrase <a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0034583/quotes" title="Casablanca Quotes">Bogie</a>, I played it for him, so now I suppose I might as well play it for you.</p>
<p><!--more--></p>
 <span class='read-more'><a href="http://www.43folders.com/2010/10/05/distraction"><strong>read&nbsp;more&nbsp;&raquo;</strong></a></span><!-- google_ad_section_end --></div>

  	
    
 
      <div class="links clear-block clear">POSTED IN: <ul class="links inline"><li class="first blog_usernames_blog"><a href="/blog/merlin-mann" title="Read Merlin&#039;s latest blog entries." class="blog_usernames_blog">Merlin&#039;s blog</a></li>
<li class="last statistics_counter"><span class="statistics_counter">45823 reads</span></li>
</ul></div>
  
