<div class="node clear-block clear ">
    <h2 class="title"><a href="/2010/09/10/my-paladin">My Faith in Nerds: Stronger Than Any Gelatinous Cube</a></h2>
  		<span class="submitted">
  		<a href="/people/merlin-mann">Merlin Mann</a>  |  Sep 10 2010	</span>

  <div class="content"><!-- google_ad_section_start --><p><a href="http://2010.dconstruct.org/speakers/merlin-mann"><strong>dConstruct 2010: 
Merlin Mann - &#8220;Kerning, Orgasms <span class="amp">&amp;</span> Those Goddamned Japanese Toothpicks&#8221;</strong></a> (<a href="http://twitter.com/hotdogsladies/status/20657852205"><span class="caps">NSFW</span></a>)</p>

<p><object type="application/x-shockwave-flash" data="http://huffduffer.com/flash/player.swf?soundFile=http://dconstruct.s3.amazonaws.com/2010/podcast/dconstruct2010-mann.mp3" width="290" height="24"><param name="movie" value="http://huffduffer.com/flash/player.swf?soundFile=http://dconstruct.s3.amazonaws.com/2010/podcast/dconstruct2010-mann.mp3" /><param name="wmode" value="transparent" /><a href="http://huffduffer.com/dConstruct/25258"><span class="caps">ME</span> - Kerning, Orgasms And Those Goddamned Japanese Toothpicks on Huffduffer</a></object></p>

<p><a href="http://dconstruct.s3.amazonaws.com/2010/podcast/dconstruct2010-mann.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" rel="enclosure">Download the audio</a> | <a href="http://huffduffer.com/add/25258">Huffduff&nbsp;it</a></p>

<hr />

<p>Let&#8217;s be honest. I don&#8217;t go&#8230;mmmm&#8230;<em>places</em> very&nbsp;often.</p>

<p>I sit in this chair. I go to the Safeway with my daughter. Sometimes, I take the train downtown to get a haircut. I check the&nbsp;mail.</p>

<p>But, by and large, like most nerds, I&#8217;m without question, a bit of a&nbsp;shut-in.</p>

<p>Which makes it more than a little  ironic that my &#xfb01;rst trip off the North American continent brought me all the way to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brighton">Brighton, England</a>&#8217;s wonderful <a href="http://2010.dconstruct.org/">dConstruct Conference</a>.</p>

<!--more-->
 <span class='read-more'><a href="http://www.43folders.com/2010/09/10/my-paladin"><strong>read&nbsp;more&nbsp;&raquo;</strong></a></span><!-- google_ad_section_end --></div>

  	
    
 
