<p>This is a <a href="http://www.merlinmann.com/news/2010/3/12/merlin-presents-3-free-talks-at-rutgers-university.html">talk I did at Rutgers</a> earlier this month. I kinda like it, but for a weird reason. Something something, perfect storm of technology Ragnarok, and yadda yadda, I had to start the talk 20 minutes late with no slides. <em>Nothing</em>.</p>

<p>So, I&nbsp;riffed.</p>
